    {
      "name": "hiring-service",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "submit-job-application",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"jobId\": 9,\n    \"candidateId\": 1,\n    \"resume\": \"# Alice Johnson\\nSan Francisco, CA | +1-555-987-6543 | alice.johnson@example.com\\n\\n### Professional Summary\\nSenior Java Developer with 6 years of experience specializing in the design and optimization of high-traffic backend microservices. Proven track record of architecting scalable systems using Spring Boot and Java, with a demonstrated ability to improve API performance by 30%. Expert in containerization and cloud-native deployment, ready to contribute to modular microservice development at InnoCore Systems.\\n\\n### Technical Skills\\n*   **Languages:** Java\\n*   **Frameworks:** Spring Boot, Hibernate\\n*   **Cloud & Infrastructure:** AWS, Docker\\n*   **DevOps & Tools:** CI/CD Pipelines, Jenkins\\n*   **Databases:** MySQL\\n\\n### Professional Experience\\n\\n**TechSphere Inc. | Senior Java Developer**\\n*June 2019 – July 2023*\\n\\n*   Led the end-to-end design and development of backend microservices for a high-traffic e-commerce platform, utilizing Java and Spring Boot to ensure modular, maintainable architecture.\\n*   Engineered high-performance API solutions, resulting in a 30% measurable improvement in response times and system throughput.\\n*   Leveraged Docker for containerization, streamlining deployment workflows and ensuring consistent environments across the development lifecycle.\\n*   Integrated AWS cloud services to support scalable, resilient microservice infrastructure.\\n\\n**CloudEdge Solutions | Backend Developer**\\n*May 2016 – May 2019*\\n\\n*   Developed and maintained scalable RESTful APIs, ensuring robust communication between distributed service components.\\n*   Implemented and managed CI/CD pipelines using Jenkins, significantly reducing manual deployment overhead and increasing release frequency.\\n*   Designed and optimized database schemas in MySQL to support high-concurrency data operations for enterprise-grade applications.\\n\\n### Additional Information\\n*   **Core Competencies:** Microservices Architecture, API Performance Tuning, Cloud Migration, CI/CD Implementation.\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
